I found and corrected a few bugs that kept the MATLAB toolbox from 
building correctly under linux/unix. These have been fixed in cantera-
1.3r1.tar.gz. To build the toolbox on linux, from MATLAB run 
buildux.m; to build in on windows, run buildwin.m. See the main 
README file for more information.
